{"tid":1714463,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"見無乜人開 今朝有中大義士提堂！！！","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:57:59.000Z","uid":89966,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"866a5129588ff3feeef76e71cf18bc367ac31566","tid":1714463,"uid":89966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:05.000Z","msg":"【聲援被捕中大義士】<br />\n<br />\n有至少五位前天（星期一）於校園被捕之中大同學將於星期三上庭，預計將被控暴動等罪，本會呼籲所有中大人到場聲援。聆訊詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：十一月十三日（星期三）<br />\n時間：9:30 a.m. <br />\n地點：沙田裁判法院（第一庭）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然無咩車 但大家盡做喇 唔好比義士孤寧寧應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想盡一切辦法到場聲援！！！"},{"pid":"717a942d45150dbc3eb7b3e401c78e9a4358f29e","tid":1714463,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223b2ce2c860bbaf17523efe959fcbaba17c8ab4","tid":1714463,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"079430b009bc3e5c37fabdbeeb1d7585cea9d73f","tid":1714463,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"沙田柚被罷工去聲援<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e0a49f77dc5284d0d5ddcc17852ef070101fa6","tid":1714463,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a>"},{"pid":"298cf61548db9bb8f0783b895839dbf8254bb530","tid":1714463,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"tui<im